<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner container">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <p class="footer-note">
        Every score on this page is accompanied by its source and methodology.
        Where data is unavailable, estimates are clearly marked and the
        reasoning documented. Corrections and contributions are welcome.
      </p>
      <p class="footer-meta">
        Scores are computed from 19 orthogonal difficulty dimensions.
        The composite ranking uses a weighted average; individual axis
        weights are defined in code and open to scrutiny.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="footer-copyright">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: var(--space-16);
    margin-top: var(--space-24);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: var(--content-max);
  }

  .footer-note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .footer-meta {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .footer-copyright {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
